data.description: This stunning 4 bedroom, 2 story home is the epitome of luxurious living. Situated on a peaceful cul-de-sac, it offers a generous 2,891 square feet of well-designed living space that provides ample room for relaxation and entertainment. As soon as you step inside, you're welcomed by an inviting foyer that leads to the spacious open concept living area. The main floor features a stylishly designed kitchen with modern appliances and ample storage space. Upstairs, you'll find four generously sized bedrooms, including a primary suite that is a haven of comfort. Outside, the backyard oasis is a private sanctuary culminates in a sparkling pool / spa, providing endless opportunities for outdoor enjoyment.  this home offers a sense of tranquility while still being conveniently close to nearby amenities, schools, and parks. Don't miss the chance to experience modern living at its finest in this thoughtfully designed property.
